<taxonomicName authorityName="Merriam" authorityYear="1886" box="[1187,1378,2882,2915]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="164" pageNumber="927" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="ciliolabrum">M. ciliolabrum</taxonomicName>
. Morphology and morphometric characters support its full species status. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
